# contract values, names, and internal hourly rates. NEVER commit to a public repo.
.claude/skills/proposal/references/

# Internal marketing strategy — positioning, GTM playbooks, channel plans,
# competitive analysis, ICP targeting, budgets, and funnel/KPI data. Competitive
# and commercially sensitive. Lives in the repo for working use but is NEVER
# committed to this PUBLIC repo.
marketing/

# Productized "agency memory" template — the replicable project-based file/logic
# structure (design.md → records → AI-generated content) packaged as a sellable
# product for real-estate agencies. Internal product IP. Local working use only,
# NEVER committed to this PUBLIC repo.
agency/
